sentences.english: The theory of yin and yang serves to explain the organic structure physiologicing changes of the human body.
sentences.chinese: 五行学说能够评释人体的生理功效和病理形态。

sentences.english: Historiographers' expertise was the knowledge background of the Yin-Yang school.
sentences.chinese: 史官的王官之学是阴阳五行家的知识背景。

sentences.english: In the theory of five elements, gold and white, the color is a metallic luster.
sentences.chinese: 在五行学说中，金为白，乃金属光泽之色。

sentences.english: The ostracon has 5 lines of text in black ink.
sentences.chinese: 古陶片上有黑墨水写的五行字。

sentences.english: Promotion and restriction among the five elements are the basic conditions for normal physiological activities of the body.
sentences.chinese: 五行的相生相克，是人体正常生理活动的基本条件。

sentences.english: Theory of five elements has some value by its significance of methodology.
sentences.chinese: 五行学说的价值主要在于其方法论意义。

sentences.english: Yang house FS's theory is all based on I Ching, Yin Yang and the changes in 5 elements.
sentences.chinese: 阳宅风水的理论依据，不离易经阴阳五行的变化。

sentences.english: Twelve-style Boxing is advanced content for further improvement after Wuxing Quan (Five-element Boxing). During exercises, we just require true meanings not alike shapes.
sentences.chinese: 十二形拳是在五行拳之后为进一步提高的进阶内容。

sentences.english: The theory of five elements is a main clue of the doctrine of viscera-state of CM (chinese Medicine).
sentences.chinese: 五行学说是中医藏象理论的主要基础之一。

sentences.english: Will someone please help me fill in the blanks in the limerick?
sentences.chinese: 有人帮我把五行诗的空填上吗？

sentences.english: The exercise is originated from the doctrines of TCM Yin Yang Five Elements Balancing and main and collateral channels.
sentences.chinese: 此功法结合了中医阴阳五行平衡和奇正相生学说。

sentences.english: Or God will toss off a limerick for your pleasure.
sentences.chinese: 或者上帝为了使你高兴而抛出一首五行打油诗。

sentences.english: In positioning the eight trigrams, it was much possible that the cyclic producing between the five elements had been taken into consideration.
sentences.chinese: 在卦位的安排中，很可能已考虑到五行的循环相生。

sentences.english: However, the seismic idea of the ruling class was Yin, Yang and the Five Elements and the idea of heavenly punishment.
sentences.chinese: 但居于社会统治地位的地震理念是阴阳五行和天诫观。

sentences.english: Since monkeys belong to the metal family in the Chinese zodiac, this name is perfect for your fair-haired daughter.
sentences.chinese: 猴子归属五行中的金，因此是很适合千金女儿的。

sentences.english: Any one of the five elements has two aspects-being restricted and restricting.
sentences.chinese: 五行中的任何之一都有克我和我克两方面性质。
